This study mainly evaluate the clinical effect of Apatinib in the treatment of patients with pulmonary metastasis of hepatocellular carcinoma.

Half of participants will receive Apatinib and transcatheter arterial chemoembolization (TACE) therapy in combination,while the other half will receive TACE therapy alone.

